[jbx://<name>]
api_url = Joe Sandbox Cloud or On-premise installations of Joe Sandbox: HTTP(S) Endpoint
api_key = To generate an API key, go to the "User settings" section in the User menu and select the "API Key" tab.
minimum_web_id = Will only download reports with an ID that is greater or equal than the ID you enter (defaults to 0).
http_https_proxy = Use HTTP / HTTPS Proxy.
verify_ssl = Verify SSL parameter for JBX REST API